{"prayers":[{"phelps":"AB02304TST","text":"Nu vo ada han e cuda e Tanawa Tanawa e wap pie-it nush ta Weed cada my a too Wee a Ma tu queet me quash  me quash cada e auta quan eada we how ta quan Kaden ought to quan qua e hoeta quan sa Wee e whan e cua Cada oo we qad me on ich, e Wab wut e Na did quay, e New casa e wa nu in.\n\n* I bear witness, O my God, that Thou hast created me to know Thee and to worship Thee. I testify, at this moment, to my powerlessness and to Thy might, to my poverty and to Thy wealth.\n* There is none other God but Thee, the Help in Peril, the Self-Subsisting.","source":"bahaiprayers.net","version":"246ca368-d0c6-4372-b545-7bd86aee1c68","book_cats":{"ar":{"cat":"النيروز","cat_order":27,"order_in_cat":4},"ar-translit":{"cat":"النيروز","cat_order":27,"order_in_cat":4},"bn":{"cat":"মহান বা’ব-এর জন্মদিনের ফলকলিপি","cat_order":28,"order_in_cat":1},"bs":{"cat":"Duhovno Vijeće","cat_order":6,"order_in_cat":1},"cy":{"cat":"Dawn","cat_order":3,"order_in_cat":1},"de":{"cat":"Das mittlere Pflichtgebet","cat_order":9,"order_in_cat":1},"en":{"cat":"Birth of The Báb","cat_order":8,"order_in_cat":2},"eu":{"cat":"Gorespen Jainkoari","cat_order":8,"order_in_cat":3},"fa":{"cat":"الواح ایام صیام","cat_order":3,"order_in_cat":2},"fa-translit":{"cat":"الواح ایام صیام","cat_order":3,"order_in_cat":2},"ht":{"cat":"Priyè pou Fanm","cat_order":37,"order_in_cat":2},"is":{"cat":"Lofgjörð og þökk","cat_order":21,"order_in_cat":7},"kl":{"cat":"Aalajaassuseq","order_in_cat":1},"lg":{"cat":"OKUSONYIYIBWA","cat_order":20,"order_in_cat":1},"lt":{"cat":"Išbandymai ir sunkumai","cat_order":5,"order_in_cat":3},"ml":{"cat":"പ്രബോധനം","cat_order":21,"order_in_cat":7},"nl":{"cat":"Lof en dankbaarheid","cat_order":26,"order_in_cat":6},"no":{"cat":"Besøkelsens tavle","cat_order":7,"order_in_cat":1},"pl":{"cat":"Ornamenty","cat_order":21,"order_in_cat":1},"ro":{"cat":"Zilele Intercalare","cat_order":48,"order_in_cat":2}},"translations":[{"language":"cy","lang_name":"Welsh"},{"langua